you already know her fake identity as a talented woman.

566
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:39,670
Yes.

567
00:30:39,690 --> 00:30:41,040
I'm here for this.

568
00:30:41,230 --> 00:30:43,520
I'm afraid the Vice Censor-in-Chief Du is secretly scheming,

569
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:47,120
so it's likely that Manyi's secret will be exposed to the public.

570
00:30:47,410 --> 00:30:48,340
I have an idea.

571
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,110
What is it?

572
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,170
Mr. Wen, please go ahead.

573
00:30:50,170 --> 00:30:51,060
Do you know that

574
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:54,550
magnets can both attract

575
00:30:54,860 --> 00:30:56,060
