576
00:30:56,850 --> 00:30:57,960
I see.

577
00:30:58,580 --> 00:31:00,200
Place a magnet

578
00:31:00,770 --> 00:31:02,230
at the bottom of the wine cup

579
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:05,360
and then placed a repelling magnet at Manyi's location.

580
00:31:05,430 --> 00:31:06,580
In this way,

581
00:31:06,620 --> 00:31:08,850
Manyi will be safe.

582
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:13,940
You two are smart.

583
00:31:14,090 --> 00:31:15,380
Not bad.

584
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:18,000
His Majesty held the Poetry Competition today,

585
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,920
yet Miss Cheng didn't have a chance to compete.

586
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,410
What a disappointment.

587
00:31:22,450 --> 00:31:24,790
Am I right?

588
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:26,060
Yes.

589
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:27,300
What?

590
00:31:28,660 --> 00:31:29,840
This shameless old man.

591
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:31,920
Trying one scheme after another.

592
00:31:31,950 --> 00:31:33,080
What are you doing?

593
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:34,400
In my opinion,

594
00:31:35,150 --> 00:31:38,060
why don't we compose a poem impromptu?

595
00:31:38,090 --> 00:31:39,650
Point at anything

596
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:41,280
and have Miss Cheng

597
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:44,750
and the other talented people take turns composing poems.

598
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,940
If this gets out,

599
00:31:45,970 --> 00:31:48,700
it'll be a grand literary event in  our Feng State.

600
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:49,940
That makes sense.

601
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:51,820
Come, let’s welcome Miss Cheng.

602
00:31:51,850 --> 00:31:53,240
Okay.

603
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:55,010
Old Crow doesn't have moral ethics.

604
00:31:55,010 --> 00:31:56,270
He wants a wheel battle

605
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:57,980
so it will be me against all of them.

606
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:59,620
You've disgraced

607
00:31:59,650 --> 00:32:01,450
the reputation of the scholars.

608
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:06,270
